provides any kind of opportunity

01:11:03.780 --> 01:11:05.470
for an organization like Sing Out.

01:11:05.470 --> 01:11:08.980
We've talked about the blogs like
[inaudible] Monday that get put

01:11:08.980 --> 01:11:10.590
