01:11:10.590 --> 01:11:13.330
Does that help Sing Out
at all do you think?

01:11:13.330 --> 01:11:14.630
And can other --

01:11:14.630 --> 01:11:20.720
&gt;&gt; Mark Moss: Well, it
does -- here's the thing.

01:11:20.720 --> 01:11:28.220 position:56%
We monthly receive about 50,000
unique hits on the Sing Out website.

01:11:28.220 --> 01:11:32.740
These are people coming to read
news, reviews, blogs, other things.

01:11:32.740 --> 01:11:36.150 position:56%
But these are people that are coming
there and they're doing it for free.

01:11:36.150 --> 01:11:42.710
And converting that into a way of
beig able to generate the income,

01:11:42.710 --> 01:11:47.430
even the pay for the basic
costs of running the website,

01:11:47.430 --> 01:11:53.570
