and the SSL certificates

01:11:53.570 --> 01:11:57.770
and renewing our URL's
and things like that is --

01:11:57.770 --> 01:12:00.160
that money's got to
come from some place.

01:12:00.160 --> 01:12:05.690
Not to forget the fact that
when we're publishing reviews

01:12:05.690 --> 01:12:09.890
that are written by somebody
as somebody that's coming

01:12:09.890 --> 01:12:13.570 position:56%
from a tradition of worker's rights,
I don't like running the stuff

01:12:13.570 --> 01:12:15.470
and not being able to pay people.

01:12:15.470 --> 01:12:20.730
So we were trying to pay a small,
infinitesibly small amount of money

01:12:20.730 --> 01:12:23.710
to somebody who writes a review
and puts it on the Sing Out site,

01:12:23.710 --> 01:12:25.280
but there's not a way
of making that happen.

01:12:25.280 --> 01:12:29.630
Now, what we're hoping
to do going forward,

01:12:29.630 --> 01:12:32.170
I mentioned that there's
a digitizing project

01:12:32.170 --> 01:12:37.320
